    <section class="page-hero"><div class="container"><div class="breadcrumbs"><a href="/">Home</a> / Process</div><span class="eyebrow">How the work happens</span><h1>A disciplined path from idea to decision.</h1><p class="lead">The process is built to protect your judgment. Fast enough to move, structured enough to avoid false confidence.</p></div></section>
    <section class="section"><div class="container process-line reveal"><div class="process-step"><h3>Intake</h3><p>Submit the idea, buyer, current situation, and proposed next spend.</p></div><div class="process-step"><h3>Clarify</h3><p>We remove ambiguity around what you are actually trying to sell.</p></div><div class="process-step"><h3>Pressure-test</h3><p>We examine market logic, buyer behavior, constraints, and risks.</p></div><div class="process-step"><h3>Recommend</h3><p>You receive a written decision memo with your next best move.</p></div><div class="process-step"><h3>Sequence</h3><p>If the idea earns commitment, we help define the next practical step.</p></div></div></section>
    <section class="section dark-band"><div class="container split"><div class="reveal"><span class="eyebrow">Operating principle</span><h2>Do not scale confidence. Scale evidence.</h2><p class="lead">A clean design can make a weak idea feel real. A strong process forces the idea to earn commitment.</p></div><div class="card reveal"><h3>What this prevents</h3><ul class="check-list"><li>Spending before the buyer is clear</li><li>Confusing branding with validation</li><li>Building workflows around untested assumptions</li><li>Hiring or buying tools before the model is ready</li></ul></div></div></section>
    <section class="section-tight"><div class="container cta-panel reveal"><h2>Ready for a diagnostic?</h2><p class="lead">Submit the idea. Get clarity. Move with discipline.</p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/book/">Book Your OVA</a></div></section>

